Interface DsaBST<ElemType>

Type Parameters:
ElemType - the type of elements held in this binary search tree. The elements must either:
  • Implement the Comparable interface to define a natural ordering, or
  • Be compatible with a custom Comparator provided by the implementation.
All Superinterfaces:
DsaTree<ElemType>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DsaBinarySearchTree
public interface DsaBST<ElemType> extends DsaTree<ElemType>
A generic interface for implementing a Binary Search Tree (BST).
